%5B%7B%22title%22%3A%22'White%20Lotus'%20star%20Jason%20Isaacs%20reflected%20on%20managing%20money%20'immaturely.'%20A%20financial%20planner%20breaks%20down%20how%20to%20avoid%20doing%20the%20same.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Jason%20Isaacs%20talking%20on%20the%20phone%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F685170ef85e81483682c3a28%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJason%20Isaacs%20in%20%26quot%3BThe%20White%20Lotus.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3EHBO%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EJason%20Isaacs%20said%20he's%20spent%20%26quot%3Bpretty%20much%20everything%26quot%3B%20he's%20earned%20as%20a%20TV%20and%20movie%20star.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIsaacs%20said%20he%20%26quot%3Bimmaturely%26quot%3B%20matched%20his%20spending%20and%20income%2C%20so%20he%20hasn't%20saved%20as%20expected.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EA%20financial%20planner%20told%20Business%20Insider%20how%20to%20avoid%20lifestyle%20creep.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20a%20movie%20star%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthe-white-lotus-cast-salaries-jason-isaacs-reveals-pay-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EJason%20Isaacs%3C%2Fa%3E%20says%20his%20financial%20situation%20isn't%20what%20you'd%20expect.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPeople%20will%20think%20I%20have%20huge%20stockpiles%20of%20money%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20%26quot%3BWhite%20Lotus%26quot%3B%20star%20told%20Vulture%20in%20an%20interview%20published%20on%20June%2016.%20%26quot%3BBut%20sadly%2C%20what%20I've%20done%20rather%20immaturely%20is%20expand%20my%20outgoings%20to%20match%20my%20incomings%20and%20pretty%20much%20spent%20everything%20I've%20earned%20over%20the%20years.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20English%20actor%20has%20more%20than%20168%20credits%20on%20IMDB%20dating%20back%20to%201988%2C%20including%20iconic%20roles%20such%20as%20Lucius%20Malfoy%20in%20the%20Harry%20Potter%20film%20adaptations%20and%20Col.%20William%20Tavington%20in%20the%202000%20hit%20%26quot%3BThe%20Patriot.%26quot%3B%20But%20while%20Isaacs%20has%20long%20enjoyed%20a%20high-powered%20and%20lucrative%20career%20%E2%80%94%20Business%20Insider%20previously%20reported%20he%2C%20and%20every%20other%20top-billed%20actor%20on%20the%20show%2C%20earned%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthe-white-lotus-cast-salary-non-negotiable-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%2440%2C000%20per%20episode%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20%26quot%3BWhite%20Lotus%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20his%20admission%20is%20indicative%20of%20a%20common%20financial%20misstep%20that%20plagues%20high-earners%3A%20lifestyle%20creep.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20really%20common%20to%20have%20lifestyle%20creep%2C%20and%20it's%20basically%20this%20phenomenon%3A%20When%20you%20earn%20more%20money%2C%20you%20spend%20more%20money%2C%26quot%3B%20Robert%20Persichitte%2C%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Finvesting%2Fcfp%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ecertified%20financial%20planner%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BPeople%20will%20see%20extra%20money%20in%20their%20bank%20account%2C%20and%20then%20they'll%20spend%20it%2C%20and%20then%20they%20get%20used%20to%20it%2C%20and%20it%20gets%20kind%20of%20locked%20into%20your%20lifestyle%20%E2%80%94%20and%20it%20becomes%20really%2C%20really%20difficult%20to%20get%20out%20of%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERepresentatives%20for%20Isaacs%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20from%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2250368bff-fdde-4fde-804f-3c94740b91d9%5C%22%3E'Do%20you%20want%20to%20be%20rich%2C%20or%20do%20you%20want%20to%20be%20wealthy%3F'%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fbanking%2Flifestyle-creep%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ELifestyle%20creep%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20most%20insidious%20when%20you%20begin%20spending%20your%20extra%20income%20on%20big-ticket%20items%20like%20expensive%20cars%2C%20fancy%20homes%2C%20or%20recurring%20subscription%20expenses%20like%20gym%20memberships%2C%20Persichitte%20said.%20That's%20not%20to%20say%20more%20modest%20luxuries%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Elike%20spa%20services%20or%20a%20trendy%20wardrobe%20can't%20add%20up%2C%20but%20he%20said%20those%20types%20of%20transactions%20are%20easier%20to%20stop%20splurging%20on%20if%20your%20financial%20situation%20changes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20very%20common%20scenario%3A%20You%20get%20somebody%20who%20has%20their%20first%20high-paying%20job%2C%20and%20they%20get%20excited%2C%20they%20go%20out%20and%20spend%20it%2C%20and%20then%20about%20six%20months%20later%2C%20they%20realize%20they%20hate%20that%20high-paying%20job%2C%26quot%3B%20Persichitte%20said.%20%26quot%3BIf%20you%20bought%20a%20new%20car%20or%20bought%20a%20new%20house%2C%20that%20is%20a%20very%2C%20very%20difficult%20decision%20to%20walk%20back.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIsaacs%20is%20far%20from%20the%20only%20celebrity%20to%20experience%20a%20problem%20with%20lifestyle%20creep.%20Al%20Pacino%2C%20in%20his%202024%20autobiography%2C%20said%20he%20went%20from%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fal-pacino-sonny-boy-wealth-money-scarface-hollywood-broke-sandler-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%2450%20million%20fortune%20to%20%26quot%3Bbroke%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%20because%20he%20didn't%20control%20his%20spending.%20Other%20stars%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0from%20Michael%20Jackson%20to%20Mike%20Tyson%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0have%20also%20racked%20up%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frich-famous-celebrities-who-lost-all-their-money-2018-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Etremendous%20amounts%20of%20debt%3C%2Fa%3E%20despite%20having%20multimillion-dollar%20incomes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20it%20may%20be%20tempting%20to%20adopt%20a%20more%20lavish%20lifestyle%20or%20emulate%20your%20favorite%20celebrity's%20spending%20habits%20if%20you%20receive%20a%20promotion%20or%20financial%20windfall%2C%20Persichitte%20cautions%20against%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPersichitte%20recalled%20a%202008%20Time%20interview%20with%20Flo%20Rida%2C%20in%20which%20the%20rapper%20said%20mogul%20Rick%20Ross%20advised%20that%2C%20in%20order%20to%20make%20more%20money%2C%20Flo%20Rida%20should%20spend%20%26quot%3Bwith%20the%20confidence%20of%20someone%20who%20knows%20he's%20going%20to%20make%20a%20lot%20more.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20wouldn't%20recommend%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20Persichitte%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20the%20logic%20to%20me%20is%3A%20Do%20you%20want%20to%20be%20rich%2C%20or%20do%20you%20want%20to%20be%20wealthy%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20difference%20is%20that%20a%20rich%20person's%20financial%20situation%20hinges%20on%20their%20next%20paycheck%2C%20which%20means%20a%20job%20loss%20or%20emergency%20or%20an%20impending%20prison%20sentence%20%E2%80%94%20which%20was%20likely%20in%20the%20future%20for%20Isaacs'%20character%20in%20%26quot%3BWhite%20Lotus%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0could%20make%20it%20all%20crumble.%20In%20comparison%2C%20Persichitte%20said%2C%20a%20wealthy%20person%20has%20long-term%20stability%20because%20they've%20prioritized%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbest-investments-ever-average-americans-stock-market-real-estate-wealth-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Esound%20investments%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20allow%20them%20more%20control%20over%20their%20finances.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20easiest%20way%20to%20avoid%20lifestyle%20creep%20is%20to%20have%20a%20plan%20for%20your%20money%20so%20it's%20not%20just%20sitting%20in%20your%20bank%20account%2C%20Persichitte%20said.%20Whether%20that%20be%20a%20401(k)%20or%20locking%20some%20portion%20of%20your%20funds%20away%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fcertificates-of-deposit%5C%22%2