3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdeloitte-accenture-job-fears-doge-consulting-contracts-trump-musk-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAccenture%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20giving%20consulting%20a%20new%20name%3A%20%26quot%3Breinvention%20services.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20global%20consulting%20firm%20reported%20its%20earnings%20on%20Friday%2C%20highlighting%20a%20generally%20positive%20performance%20for%20the%20third%20fiscal%20quarter%20of%202025.%20The%20firm%20reported%20revenue%20of%20%2417.7%20billion%2C%20an%208%25%20increase%20from%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ethis%20time%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20new%20bookings%20were%20down%206%25%20compared%20to%20the%20third%20quarter%20in%202024%2C%20Accenture%20CEO%20Julie%20Sweet%20told%20CNBC%20on%20Friday%20that%20the%20firm%20was%20%26quot%3Breally%20pleased%26quot%3B%20with%20its%20bookings%20and%20that%20demand%20for%20its%20services%20could%20be%20seen%20in%20its%20revenue.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESweet%20said%20on%20the%20earnings%20call%20that%20AI%20is%20the%20firm's%20strongest%20bet%20for%20creating%20new%20demand%20and%20that%20to%20maximize%20AI's%20potential%2C%20the%20firm%20is%20consolidating%20its%20strategy%2C%20consulting%2C%20song%2C%20technology%2C%20and%20operations%20services%20into%20a%20single%20unit%20known%20as%20%26quot%3Breinvention%20services%2C%26quot%3B%20starting%20September%201.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20we're%20going%20to%20do%20now%20is%20make%20it%20even%20easier%20to%20bring%20those%20solutions%2C%20embed%20data%20and%20AI%2C%20so%20we%20can%20really%20scale%20across%20our%20client%20base%20and%20into%20new%20markets%20using%20our%20reinvention%20services%2C%26quot%3B%20Sweet%20told%20CNBC.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhat%20consultants%20do%20sometimes%20needs%20to%20be%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eexplained%2C%20and%20%26quot%3Breinvention%20services%26quot%3B%20is%20no%20exception.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20both%20her%20CNBC%20interview%20and%20the%20earnings%20call%20on%20Friday%2C%20Sweet%20shared%20several%20examples%20of%20the%20company's%20AI-powered%20reinvention%20work%2C%20which%20%E2%80%94%20following%20its%20reorganization%20%E2%80%94%20the%20firm%20will%20be%20able%20to%20execute%20more%20efficiently%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20one%20example%2C%20she%20said%20Accenture%20is%20working%20with%20Italian%20shipbuilding%20company%20Fincantieri%20to%20launch%20the%20first%20AI-powered%20ship%20in%202025.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESweet%20told%20CNBC%20that%20the%20ship%20will%20be%20able%20to%20%26quot%3Bpredict%20its%20maintenance%2C%20manage%20its%20energy%20use%20on%20its%20own%2C%20and%20talk%20to%20the%20dock%26quot%3B%20before%20it%20arrives%20at%20its%20destination.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20Accenture's%20work%20to%20modernize%20the%20manufacturing%20process%20for%20Bel%2C%20maker%20of%20Laughing%20Cow%20cheese%2C%20would%20also%20fall%20under%20this%20new%20department%2C%20as%20would%20its%20collaboration%20with%20Brazilian%20mining%20company%20Vale%20to%20expedite%20environmental%20licensing%20and%20permits.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20also%20said%20the%20firm%20is%20creating%20AI-generated%203D%20avatars%20of%20physical%20products%20for%20coffee%20brands%20like%20Nescaf%C3%A9%2C%20Dolce%20Gusto%2C%20and%20Nespresso%20to%20reduce%20the%20time%20and%20cost%20of%20developing%20marketing%20campaigns%2C%20which%20would%20also%20fall%20under%20the%20new%20reinvention%20services%20department.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESweet%20told%20CNBC%20that%20AI%20can%20be%20a%20%26quot%3Btool%26quot%3B%20to%20help%20companies%20navigate%20the%20future%2C%20but%20to%20reap%20the%20benefits%2C%20it%20will%20also%20need%20to%20be%20%26quot%3Bdisruptive.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Faccenture-ai-reinvention-services-earnings-ceo-julie-sweet-2025-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1750452438000%2C%22visual%22%3