%252Ftech%252Fverizon-review%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.verizon.com%252Fcoverage-map%252F%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EVerizon's%20coverage%20map%3C%2Fa%3E%20can%20give%20you%20an%20idea%2C%20it's%20not%20always%20accurate%20%E2%80%94%20even%20if%20it%20shows%20your%20area%20has%20coverage%2C%20it%20doesn't%20reflect%20whether%20it%20supports%20sufficient%20data%20speeds.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Verizon's%20coverage%20map%20for%20Alaska%20as%20of%20early%202025.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F680bcfacc6ad288d147f3267%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EScreenshot%20of%20Verizon's%20coverage%20map.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20I%20live%20in%20a%20specific%20pocket%20of%20a%20sprawling%20Connecticut%20mid-country%20suburb%2C%20and%20I%20face%20coverage%20issues%20with%20all%20carriers%2C%20including%20Verizon%20(I%20recognize%20the%20irony%20for%20a%20reporter%20like%20myself%20writing%20carrier%20reviews).%20While%20I%20can%20get%20two%20bars%20of%20Verizon%20LTE%20coverage%20at%20home%2C%20video%20streaming%20on%20data%20is%20impossible%2C%20and%20phone%20calls%20are%20just%20about%20acceptable.%20I%20am%20strongly%20reliant%20on%20WiFi%20for%20internet%20and%20WiFi%20calling%20at%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Verizon's%20coverage%20map%20for%20Hawaii%20as%20of%20early%202025.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F680bcfc9c6ad288d147f3270%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EScreenshot%20of%20Verizon's%20coverage%20map.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIndeed%2C%20I%20can%20forget%20about%20the%20lightest%20data%20usage%20at%20home%2C%20inside%2C%20or%20outside.%20Even%20sending%20data-based%20texts%20like%20iMessages%20or%20WhatsApp%20(not%20SMS%20texts)%20requires%20me%20to%20stand%20on%20a%20low%20wall%20outside%20the%20house%2C%20reaching%20for%20the%20sky%20with%20my%20phone%2C%20when%20there's%20an%20internet%20outage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EVerizon%20will%20sometimes%20offer%20a%20promotion%20for%20a%20free%20network%20extender%20(usually%20%24250).%20I've%20used%20a%20similar%20variant%20to%20the%20current%20model%20in%20the%20past%2C%20and%20while%20it%20provides%20a%20strong%20LTE%20signal%20for%20phone%20calls%2C%20texts%2C%20and%20data%2C%20it's%20reliant%20on%20an%20internet%20connection.%20That's%20not%20helpful%20to%20anyone%20if%20your%20ISP%20is%20facing%20an%20internet%20outage.%20The%20range%20extender%20I%20used%20in%20the%20past%20also%20required%20to%20be%20installed%20near%20a%20window%20so%20it%20could%20get%20a%20GPS%20connection%2C%20which%20isn't%20ideal%20depending%20on%20the%20location%20of%20your%20router.%20Overall%2C%20I%20don't%20recommend%20the%20network%20extender%2C%20especially%20at%20%24250.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20flipside%2C%20Verizon%20has%20coverage%20in%20a%20remote%20area%20of%20the%20Adirondacks%20region%20in%20upstate%20NY%20I%20visit%20annually%2C%20which%20is%20one%20of%20the%20reasons%20I%20picked%20Verizon%20over%20others.%20Indeed%2C%20I%20can%20stream%20videos%20on%20Verizon's%20networks%20in%20this%20remote%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20be%20sure%2C%20this%20kind%20of%20experience%20can%20be%20had%20with%20any%20carrier%2C%20so%20as%20I%20mentioned%20earlier%2C%20it's%20best%20to%20find%20out%20whether%20Verizon%20works%20well%20for%20people%20in%20the%20areas%20you%20often%20visit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2247c63e2e-7ff3-488a-a56a-49c19da65f3d%5C%22%3ECustomer%20support%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20can%20reach%20Verizon%20customer%20support%20via%20online%20chat%2C%20text%20message%2C%20at%20a%20first-party%20or%20authorized%20physical%20location%2C%20and%20over%20the%20phone.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222400%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20original%20photo%20of%20an%20Apple%20iPhone%2016%20Pro%20Max%20held%20in%20a%20hand%20running%20the%20Verizon%20app's%20chat%20support%20feature.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F680fe0d33fe8d392836448f7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221800%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EAntonio%20Villas-Boas%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EVerizon's%20customer%20support%20is%20typical%20for%20a%20large%20company%20%E2%80%94%20remote%20support%20options%20usually%20start%20with%20automated%20or%20AI%20assistance%2C%20but%20you%20can%20say%20or%20type%20%26quot%3Brepresentative%26quot%3B%20to%20get%20a%20real%20human%20being.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20depends%20on%20the%20day%2C%20but%20it%20can%20take%20anywhere%20from%20less%20than%20a%20minute%20to%20%26quot%3Ba%20while%26quot%3B%20to%20reach%20a%20human.%20Verizon%20offers%20a%20call-back%20feature%20that%20lets%20you%20hang%20up%20and%20keep%20your%20place%20in%20line%2C%20and%20a%20customer%20service%20representative%20will%20call%20you%20back%20when%20it's%20your%20turn.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20had%20all%20my%20minor%20issues%20in%20recent%20memory%20addressed%2C%20and%20it%20can%20take%20five%20minutes%20(after%20reaching%20a%20human)%20to%20a%20couple%20of%20hours%2C%20depending%20on%20the%20issue%2C%20day%2C%20or%20representative.%20Overall%2C%20I%20have%20been%20happy%20with%20Verizon's%20support.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2273cd784a-8d5a-4fd0-b3ee-c9e423367f81%5C%22%3EShould%20you%20sign%20up%20for%20Verizon%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAnyone%20living%20in%20and%20visiting%20places%20with%20good%20Verizon%20coverage%20will%20be%20happy%20with%20its%20data%20speeds%20and%20overall%20experience.%20However%2C%20it%20might%20not%20offer%20the%20best%20value%20for%20every%20type%20of%20user%20or%20account.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EVerizon%20offers%20the%20best%20value%20for%20customers%20with%20four%20lines%20or%20more%2C%20making%20it%20a%20great%20option%20for%20families%20and%20friend%20groups.%20If%20you%20have%20fewer%20than%20four%20lines%2C%20you%20should%20check%20out%20Verizon's%20subsidiary%2C%20Visible.%20Our%20guide%20provides%20a%20detailed%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fvisible-vs-verizon%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EVisible%20vs.%20Verizon%3C%2Fa%3E%20comparison.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20only%20one%20good%20reason%20to%20opt%20for%20a%20Verizon%20prepaid%20plan%3A%20the%20potential%20to%20get%20better%20support%20from%20a%20human%20being%2C%20whether%20on%20the%20phone%2C%20online%2C%20or%20at%20a%20physical%20location.%20Otherwise%2C%20Visible's%20prepaid%20plans%20offer%20significantly%20better%20value.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EVerizon%20offers%20the%20best%20perks%20in%20the%20industry%20with%20its%20discounts%20for%20popular%20third-party%20services.%20However%2C%20don't%20base%20your%20decision%20on%20perks%20alone.%20Rather%2C%20you%20should%20primarily%20pick%20a%20carrier%20based%20on%20coverage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EDoes%20Verizon%20have%20a%20senior%20plan%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EYes%20and%20no.%20Verizon%20offers%20plans%20for%20seniors%2055%20or%20older%20who%20live%20%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3Ein%20Florida%20only%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%20These%20plans%20include%20unlimited%20talk%2C%20text%2C%20and%20deprioritized%20data.%20They%20also%20include%20a%20mobile%20hotspot%2C%20but%20at%20an%20unusably%20slow%20600%20Kbps%20(too%20slow%20to%20be%20of%20%3Cem%3Eany%3C%2Fem%3E%20use).%20In%20most%20cases%2C%20we'd%20rather%20recommend%20Verizon's%20Unlimited%20Welcome%20for%20seniors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20a%20single%20line%2C%20its%20%2462%20monthly%20cost%20is%20marginally%20less%20than%20Verizon's%20base%20%2465%20Unlimited%20Welcome%20plan.%20For%20two%20lines%20at%20%2442%20each%20a%20month%2C%20you%20could%20argue%20it's%20worth%20going%20for%20compared%20to%20the%20Unlimited%20Welcom