expressing%20their%20thoughts%2C%20feelings%2C%20and%20needs%20clearly%2C%20confidently%2C%20and%20respectfully.%20It%20is%20designed%20to%20strike%20a%20balance%20between%20passivity%20and%20aggression%2C%20thus%2C%20enabling%20people%20to%20stand%20up%20for%20themselves.%20Whether%20in%20personal%20relationships%20or%20professional%20settings%2C%20assertiveness%20is%20about%20being%20honest%20and%20direct%20while%20maintaining%20respect%20and%20empathy.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAt%20its%20core%2C%20assertiveness%20training%20teaches%20people%20how%20to%20say%20%E2%80%9Cno%E2%80%9D%20without%20guilt%2C%20express%20opinions%20without%20fear%2C%20handle%20criticism%20constructively%2C%20and%20set%20healthy%20personal%20and%20professional%20boundaries.%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAssertiveness%20training%20is%20frequently%20incorporated%20into%20therapeutic%20contexts%20such%20as%20Cognitive%20Behavioural%20Therapy%20(CBT)%2C%20social%20skills%20groups%2C%20and%20trauma%20recovery%20programmes.%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20Dr%20Bhargava%20shares%20the%20story%20of%20a%20patient%20from%20the%20queer%20community%20diagnosed%20with%20Generalised%20Anxiety%20Disorder.%20%E2%80%9CDuring%20evaluation%2C%20it%20became%20clear%20that%20gender-related%20confusion%20and%20societal%20pressure%20in%20adolescence%20played%20a%20huge%20role%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETreatment%20involved%20more%20than%20just%20medication.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20initiated%20a%20personalised%20psychosocial%20intervention%20focused%20on%20tackling%20internalised%20helplessness%20and%20cognitive%20distortions.%20It%20was%20about%20building%20resilience%20and%20not%20erasing%20identity.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F0